main huun paanavaali bina dukaan vaali
are saare gaanv ke labon pe chamake hamare paan ki laali
dilli ho madraas ho chaahe bambayi ho ya kalakatta
sau rogon ki ek dava hai ye hare paan ka patta
ho babuwa khaata ja ik paan paan mein hamare badi hai jaan
hamare paan pe to qurbaan hai saara hindustaan
ho babuwa ho laala he raaja khaata ja ik paankhaake khile labon pe laali chehare pe chhaaye hariyaali
ek gilori chaba ke jaao hogi tum pe fida gharavaali
ek madhur muskaan se hogi har mushkil aasaan
ho babuwa khaata ja ik paanagar ho mahabuub ko manaana
leke saath paan ye jaana
saare bigade kaam banaana
hamare paan pe aashiq bachche buudhe aur javaan
ho babuwa khaata ja ik paanaha mahafil jame ho naach ya gaana
shaadi byaah ka jashn manaana
babuwa paan dabaakar jaana
saari mahafil mein chha jaana
bina paan ke to hai adhuuri har mahafil ki shaan
ho babuwa khaata ja ik paan